- Schema: Article + FAQPage (3 Qs below); strong /about/ support page for "who is Lisa Collio" AI queries

- Internal links: /about/, /buyers/, /contact/

- Primary keyword: "why Lisa Collio became a real estate agent"; secondary: "who is Lisa Collio," "Lisa Collio story"

